    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Z.O.N.A Project X - 不仅仅是一款游戏，它是一个完整的沉浸在严酷的末日世界中，您的每一个选择都可能成为决定性的。多样的后末日世界，不可预测的剧情，逼真的武器操作和危险的异常现象 - 这一切都在这款令人兴奋的游戏中等待着您。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142450/extras/62dfb35d3469bc5b01e8b1e7552fc0ae.poster.avif?t=1743350597\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142450/extras/62dfb35d3469bc5b01e8b1e7552fc0ae.webm?t=1743350597\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142450/extras/62dfb35d3469bc5b01e8b1e7552fc0ae.mp4?t=1743350597\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您准备好应对挑战了吗？准备在切尔诺贝利区域度过紧张的生存和残酷反乌托邦的探索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >剧情</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您将置身于不久的将来，当我们的地球因核武器而变得不适合生活。在这样的世界里，生存成为头等大事。而只有您可以帮助一小撮幸存的人们从不可避免的毁灭中拯救出来。所以，欢迎来到切尔诺贝利区域，在这里生存成为一种艺术，危险潜伏在每个角落。在这个世界里，没有错误的余地。此外，您必须准备好面对嗜血的怪物和贪婪的强盗。在这里，人人为己，只有您的武器才能保护您免受潜伏在每个角落的危险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142450/extras/824075e68b5f3f8a544d1b6b93a35623.poster.avif?t=1743350597\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142450/extras/824075e68b5f3f8a544d1b6b93a35623.webm?t=1743350597\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142450/extras/824075e68b5f3f8a544d1b6b93a35623.mp4?t=1743350597\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不可预测的剧情、精美的画面、各种武器、嗜血的怪物和贪婪的强盗 - 这就是您在Z.O.N.A Project X宇宙中等待着您的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142450/extras/c1492d7888a8f314ec5c3fd4418ccfc9.poster.avif?t=1743350597\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142450/extras/c1492d7888a8f314ec5c3fd4418ccfc9.webm?t=1743350597\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142450/extras/c1492d7888a8f314ec5c3fd4418ccfc9.mp4?t=1743350597\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >致命异常</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142450/extras/f84345330280dbbf714c235d345eea10.poster.avif?t=1743350597\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142450/extras/f84345330280dbbf714c235d345eea10.webm?t=1743350597\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142450/extras/f84345330280dbbf714c235d345eea10.mp4?t=1743350597\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >生存</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您将踏上一段危险的任务，探索切尔诺贝利区域，在那里，隐秘和安静是您的主要盟友。生存取决于您移动缓慢，蹲下，潜行和小心的能力。您可以从各种武器中选择，并收集战利品以变得更强大和更具抵抗力。但是，请不要忘记，致命的异常现象可能会成为您最糟糕的敌人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142450/extras/a99f03b18ed54a3ee73bf9adec6981e6.poster.avif?t=1743350597\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142450/extras/a99f03b18ed54a3ee73bf9adec6981e6.webm?t=1743350597\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142450/extras/a99f03b18ed54a3ee73bf9adec6981e6.mp4?t=1743350597\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >末日世界的严酷</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索残酷的反乌托邦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特点</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ 突袭系统。探索区域最危险的角落 — 从“秘密隧道”到“军事小镇”，那里有苏联雷达站“Дуга”，在地平线上高耸。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ 长时间的紧张生存。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ 有趣且难以预测的剧情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ 切尔诺贝利区域无情的反乌托邦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ 多样化的后末日世界，从废弃的隧道到城市建筑，具有巨大的探险潜力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ 逼真地操作各种经典和现代武器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ 危险的异常现象，阴暗的氛围和危险的强盗。</p>",
